<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>10 SPEED TRANSMISSIONS FULLER RT-610 SERIES - REMOVE - RANGE SHIFT AIR CYLINDER AND SYNCHRONIZER
        ASSEMBLIES
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="5">
        <title>RANGE SHIFT AIR CYLINDER AND SYNCHRONIZER ASSEMBLIES</title>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the bolts and air cylinder cover.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the nut and lockwasher from the air cylinder piston shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302449">Figure 49</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302449" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302449" filename="../figg13/G1302449.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 49. Remove Nut and Lockwasher From Air Cylinder Piston Shaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Use air to remove the piston (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302450">Figure 50</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302450" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302450" filename="../figg13/G1302450.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 50. Use Air to Remove Piston</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If necessary, remove the O-ring from the O.D. of the piston.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the copper seal from the shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302451">Figure 51</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302451" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302451" filename="../figg13/G1302451.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 51. Remove Copper Seal From Shaft</caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Move the synchronizer assembly, shift yoke and piston shaft forward and out of the housing
                as a complete assembly (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302452">Figure 52</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302452" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302452" filename="../figg13/G1302452.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 52. Move Synchronizer Assembly, Shift Yoke and Piston Shaft Forward and Out of Housing
            </caption>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the shaft and yoke from the synchronizer assembly.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Cut the lockwire, remove the two lockscrews and remove the yoke from the shaft (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1302453">Figure 53</hotlnk>).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <figure id="f1302453" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="g1302453" filename="../figg13/G1302453.webp" type="webp" scalefit="0"/>
            <caption>Figure 53. Remove Yoke From Shaft</caption>
        </figure>
    </svcproc>
